Text: Small file size had me wondering.  But it's unabridged:  appears to be Brilliance Audio Library Edition, 35h 16min 11sec, 24kbps, 22kHz mono.  Quality is consequently only ok, - a bit bassy and lacking the high-end clarity.  Better audio quality would have been worth the bigger download.  I'm about halfway through with no issues.  Thanks for the upload!
Thanks so much! Out of all the billions on the planet, you are the only person who has apparently uploaded this.
Thank you so much.  I live in Central America and it is near impossible to find English books.
If there is anyone out there that would please seed.  This is the "only" place I have found this book.  Thanks in advance.
